    <string name="about_summary_body">Have something to say on how to improve your local community? Action Path brings the town hall to you.\n\nCreated by the MIT Center for Civic Media, Action Path is a location-based civic engagement platform that prompts you to explore your cities and participate in governance around infrastructure issues and planning.\n\nThe current version allows you to investigate and update issues from SeeClickFix.com. We plan to expand the range of activities in future releases. Thanks for taking action!</string>

